The Postmaster of Mafdet holds an open commission for a complete navigation survey of the Southern Oasis. The oasis is a significant waypoint on the southern desert caravan routes, but the current documentation in Mafdet's harbor reference files is incomplete. Survey every accessible section of the oasis and return with a full route record so caravan operators can plan the southern approach accurately.
Your Southern Oasis survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority. The route record has been added to the southern desert corridor reference files and caravan operators have been notified of the updated documentation.

